---
title: Prawn and Greek Style Cheese Bake with toasted ciabatta
description: This recipe is simple to prepare—simply pop it all in an oven dish—but in terms of flavour, it really packs a punch. If you're a fan of meaty prawns and salty Greek style cheese then this is definitely the dish for you!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y25_R16_W24_IE_IEFS40796-2_Main_high-9fc33d3c.jpg
